metadata.name: I'm losing my mind to someone else's bullshit
metadata.description:
Is life a big scam or the society makes a meme out of it? Some people made you go crazy.

This collection is not to be taken to seriusly. 

Contraindications: depression, anxiety, convulsions, insonia, hysterical pregnancy, panic attacks, hysteria, apparent death, desire to change life and gender, hitting others and various unlisted problems.
